From 44e36f95c3b420906f3e84a8f977fb4487a87b87 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 09:18:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Rework UI entirely to Project Zero white-theme CSS

Replace all styling with the projectzero.google white-theme CSS system:
- globals.css now uses Google Sans Flex/Text/Mono, PZ colour variables,
  8-column subgrid layout, post-date fill-on-hover, hollow-text logo,
  and PZ syntax-highlight classes; adds compat rules for rehype-highlight
- layout.tsx: hollow-text logo, tagline, pure-CSS mobile nav toggle,
  PZ footer; removes ThemeToggle (light-only theme)
- All pages rewritten to PZ article/grid/post-header/post-content classes
- ThemeToggle component removed

https://claude.ai/code/session_01V6MMd4Ryg1hfxAaRPWa3as
